Independencia Seeks to Lease Slaughterhouses, Estado Reports

-- B y   L u c i a   K a s s a i
-- 
2011-10-20T11:45:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-20/independencia-seeks-to-lease-slaughterhouses-estado-reports.html
Independencia SA is seeking to lease
three slaughterhouses, one tannery, two warehouses and four
plots of land after failing to sell those assets, O Estado de S.
Paulo reported, citing a lawyer who represents cattle ranchers.  Independencia, which is under bankruptcy protection, would
pay cattle ranchers ahead of other creditors, lawyer Carlo
Daniel Coldibelli told the Sao Paulo-based newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lucia Kassai in Sao Paulo at 
 lkassai@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dale Crofts at 
 dcrofts@bloomberg.net  